{% comment %}
  CUSTOM · Acquista — homepage buy box

  Sezione custom homepage (pattern: .claude/patterns/building-custom-homepage-section.md).
  Buy box modellato sulla LP B2C (lp-offerta) ma sobrio e allineato a Dawn:
  usa i token del tema. L'add to cart usa `custom-buy-buttons`, clone scoped
  dello snippet ufficiale Dawn `buy-buttons` (<product-form> + product-form.js)
  con label custom. Vedi decision 006 e 036.

  Interattivita' (selezione variante, carousel) in assets/custom-buy-box.js, che
  aggiorna l'input name="id" del form al cambio variante.
{% endcomment %}

{{ 'custom-buy-box.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

{%- liquid
  assign product = section.settings.product
  # Locale gate: EN storefront shows English copy, everything else falls back to
  # Italian. Same convention as the homepage reviews section (custom_liquid "recensioni").
  # `assign` can't take a comparison expression directly — build the boolean via if/endif.
  assign is_en = false
  if request.locale.iso_code == 'en'
    assign is_en = true
  endif
-%}

{%- if product == blank -%}
  {%- comment -%} Editor: nessun prodotto scelto. Placeholder minimo. {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="custom-buy-box custom-buy-box--empty">
    <p>{% if is_en %}Select a product in the section settings.{% else %}Seleziona un prodotto nelle impostazioni della sezione.{% endif %}</p>
  </div>
{%- else -%}
  {%- liquid
    assign first_variant = product.selected_or_first_available_variant
    assign product_form_id = 'custom-buy-box-form-' | append: section.id

    # Rileva quale opzione e' il colore e quale la taglia, per nome (come lp-offerta).
    # Il match per nome rende la sezione indipendente dall'ordine delle opzioni.
    assign color_option = null
    assign size_option = null
    for opt in product.options_with_values
      assign oname = opt.name | downcase
      if oname contains 'color' or oname contains 'colore' or oname contains 'colour'
        assign color_option = opt
      elsif oname contains 'taglia' or oname contains 'size' or oname contains 'misura'
        assign size_option = opt
      endif
    endfor
    # Fallback taglia: prima opzione diversa dal colore.
    if size_option == null
      for opt in product.options_with_values
        if color_option == null or opt.position != color_option.position
          assign size_option = opt
          break
        endif
      endfor
    endif

  -%}

  {%- comment -%} id="acquista": ancora per link interni (es. #acquista). {%- endcomment -%}
  <custom-buy-box id="acquista" class="custom-buy-box color-{{ section.settings.color_scheme }}">

    {%- comment -%} Dati varianti Liquid -> JS (pattern blob, niente interpolazione). {%- endcomment -%}
    <script type="application/json" class="custom-buy-box__data">
      {{ product.variants | json }}
    </script>

    <div class="custom-buy-box__inner">

      {%- comment -%}
        ============ COLONNA MEDIA ============
        Carousel foto statico (fisso, non dipende da colore/taglia): scroll-snap
        nativo per lo swipe, immagini fisse in assets/ (pdp-1.png..pdp-5.png),
        non piu' variant_gallery. Click su una thumbnail scrolla al suo slide
        (data-photo-slides/data-photo-thumb, logica in custom-buy-box.js).
      {%- endcomment -%}
      <div class="custom-buy-box__media">
        <div class="custom-buy-box__slides" data-photo-slides>
          <div class="custom-buy-box__slide">
            <img
              class="custom-buy-box__pdp-image"
              src="{{ 'pdp-1.png' | asset_url }}"
              alt="{{ product.title | escape }}"
              loading="lazy"
            >
          </div>
          <div class="custom-buy-box__slide">
            <img
              class="custom-buy-box__pdp-image"
              src="{{ 'pdp-2.png' | asset_url }}"
              alt="{{ product.title | escape }}"
              loading="lazy"
            >
          </div>
          <div class="custom-buy-box__slide">
            <img
              class="custom-buy-box__pdp-image"
              src="{{ 'pdp-3.png' | asset_url }}"
              alt="{{ product.title | escape }}"
              loading="lazy"
            >
          </div>
          <div class="custom-buy-box__slide">
            <img
              class="custom-buy-box__pdp-image"
              src="{{ 'pdp-4.png' | asset_url }}"
              alt="{{ product.title | escape }}"
              loading="lazy"
            >
          </div>
          <div class="custom-buy-box__slide">
            <img
              class="custom-buy-box__pdp-image"
              src="{{ 'pdp-5.png' | asset_url }}"
              alt="{{ product.title | escape }}"
              loading="lazy"
            >
          </div>
          {%- comment -%}
            Slide lifestyle 6-8: le 3 foto migliori della ex sezione gallery
            (disabilitata in templates/index.json), integrate qui in coda alle
            infografiche. Ordine marketplace-standard: prima il prodotto/specs,
            poi il contesto reale. URL CDN hardcoded con <img src> (rules.md),
            ?width= per non scaricare l'originale full-size.
          {%- endcomment -%}
          <div class="custom-buy-box__slide">
            <img
              class="custom-buy-box__pdp-image"
              src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/dsc01880-migliorato-nr-1769702403-697b8403bf89b.jpg?width=1200"
              alt="{{ product.title | escape }} indossate al lavoro"
              loading="lazy"
            >
          </div>
          <div class="custom-buy-box__slide">
            <img
              class="custom-buy-box__pdp-image"
              src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/dsc01813-migliorato-nr-1769702375-697b83e7ab8e3.jpg?width=1200"
              alt="{{ product.title | escape }} dettaglio dal vivo"
              loading="lazy"
            >
          </div>
          {%- comment -%}
            Slide 8-9: lavorazione artigianale a mano (pdp-6/pdp-7 in assets/,
            da Downloads del cliente come le pdp-1..5). Prova visiva del claim
            "cucita a mano da artigiani italiani" della sezione garanzie.
          {%- endcomment -%}
          <div class="custom-buy-box__slide">
            <img
              class="custom-buy-box__pdp-image"
              src="{{ 'pdp-6.jpg' | asset_url }}"
              alt="{{ product.title | escape }} cucite a mano da artigiani italiani"
              loading="lazy"
            >
          </div>
          <div class="custom-buy-box__slide">
            <img
              class="custom-buy-box__pdp-image"
              src="{{ 'pdp-7.jpg' | asset_url }}"
              alt="Lavorazione artigianale a mano delle {{ product.title | escape }}"
              loading="lazy"
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="custom-buy-box__thumbs">
          <button type="button" class="custom-buy-box__thumb-btn is-active" data-photo-thumb="0">
            <img class="custom-buy-box__thumb" src="{{ 'pdp-1.png' | asset_url }}" alt="" loading="lazy">
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="custom-buy-box__thumb-btn" data-photo-thumb="1">
            <img class="custom-buy-box__thumb" src="{{ 'pdp-2.png' | asset_url }}" alt="" loading="lazy">
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="custom-buy-box__thumb-btn" data-photo-thumb="2">
            <img class="custom-buy-box__thumb" src="{{ 'pdp-3.png' | asset_url }}" alt="" loading="lazy">
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="custom-buy-box__thumb-btn" data-photo-thumb="3">
            <img class="custom-buy-box__thumb" src="{{ 'pdp-4.png' | asset_url }}" alt="" loading="lazy">
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="custom-buy-box__thumb-btn" data-photo-thumb="4">
            <img class="custom-buy-box__thumb" src="{{ 'pdp-5.png' | asset_url }}" alt="" loading="lazy">
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="custom-buy-box__thumb-btn" data-photo-thumb="5">
            <img class="custom-buy-box__thumb" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/dsc01880-migliorato-nr-1769702403-697b8403bf89b.jpg?width=160" alt="" loading="lazy">
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="custom-buy-box__thumb-btn" data-photo-thumb="6">
            <img class="custom-buy-box__thumb" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/dsc01813-migliorato-nr-1769702375-697b83e7ab8e3.jpg?width=160" alt="" loading="lazy">
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="custom-buy-box__thumb-btn" data-photo-thumb="7">
            <img class="custom-buy-box__thumb" src="{{ 'pdp-6.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" loading="lazy">
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="custom-buy-box__thumb-btn" data-photo-thumb="8">
            <img class="custom-buy-box__thumb" src="{{ 'pdp-7.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="" loading="lazy">
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      {%- comment -%} ============ COLONNA INFO ============ {%- endcomment -%}
      <div class="custom-buy-box__info">

        <h2 class="custom-buy-box__title">Dr Kampes — Trucker Shoes</h2>

        {%- comment -%} Recensioni fake, come la LP: 5 stelle piene + testo hardcoded. {%- endcomment -%}
        <div class="custom-buy-box__reviews">
          <span class="custom-buy-box__stars" aria-hidden="true">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span>
          <span class="custom-buy-box__reviews-text">
            {%- if is_en -%}
              4.9/5 from over 1200 satisfied truckers
            {%- else -%}
              4.9/5 da oltre 1200 camionisti soddisfatti
            {%- endif -%}
          </span>
        </div>

        {%- comment -%} Prezzo + rata raggruppati: gap stretto fra loro. {%- endcomment -%}
        <div class="custom-buy-box__price-block">
          <div class="custom-buy-box__price">
            <span class="custom-buy-box__price-current" data-price>{{ first_variant.price | money }}</span>
            <s
              class="custom-buy-box__price-compare"
              data-compare
              {% unless first_variant.compare_at_price > first_variant.price %}hidden{% endunless %}
            >{{ first_variant.compare_at_price | money }}</s>
          </div>

          {%- comment -%}
            Importo rata dinamico = prezzo variante / 3. Frase hardcoded.
            Klarna/PayPal come chip nei colori brand (testo colorato bocciato:
            il rosa Klarna su bianco non passa il contrasto; la loro linea
            guida e' proprio testo nero su pillola rosa).
          {%- endcomment -%}
          <p class="custom-buy-box__installment">
            {%- if is_en -%}
              Or <strong>3 instalments of <span data-installment>{{ first_variant.price | divided_by: 3 | money }}</span></strong> with
            {%- else -%}
              Oppure <strong>3 rate da <span data-installment>{{ first_variant.price | divided_by: 3 | money }}</span></strong> con
            {%- endif %}
            <span class="custom-buy-box__pay-badge custom-buy-box__pay-badge--klarna">Klarna</span>
            <span class="custom-buy-box__pay-badge custom-buy-box__pay-badge--paypal">PayPal</span>
          </p>
        </div>

        {%- comment -%}
          Banner spedizione: il claim piu' forte della pagina, sempre visibile
          vicino al prezzo (prima stava solo dentro un accordion chiuso).
          Copy allineato alla LP ("SPEDIZIONE GRATIS 1-2 GIORNI", lp-offerta).
          Icona camion stroke inline (le stock Dawn fill-based possono sparire
          su scheme scuri, vedi rules.md).
        {%- endcomment -%}
        <div class="custom-buy-box__shipping-banner">
          <svg class="custom-buy-box__shipping-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
            <path d="M5 18H3a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h11a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v10"/>
            <path d="M15 8h4l3 4v5a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-1"/>
            <circle cx="7.5" cy="18" r="2"/>
            <circle cx="17.5" cy="18" r="2"/>
            <path d="M9.5 18H15"/>
          </svg>
          <span>
            {%- if is_en -%}
              <strong>Free shipping, 1&ndash;2 days</strong> &middot; free returns &amp; size exchange
            {%- else -%}
              <strong>Spedizione gratis in 1-2 giorni</strong> &middot; reso e cambio taglia gratuiti
            {%- endif -%}
          </span>
        </div>

        {%- if color_option -%}
          <div class="custom-buy-box__opt" data-color-opt data-pos="{{ color_option.position | minus: 1 }}">
            <p class="custom-buy-box__opt-label">
              {{ color_option.name | escape }}: <span data-color-value>{{ color_option.selected_value | escape }}</span>
            </p>
            <div class="custom-buy-box__swatches">
              {%- for value in color_option.values -%}
                {%- comment -%}
                  Sfondo swatch: swatch Shopify se configurato, altrimenti fallback
                  per i colori noti del prodotto (lo store non ha sempre gli swatch).
                {%- endcomment -%}
                {%- capture sw_style -%}
                  {%- if value.swatch.color -%}--swatch:{{ value.swatch.color }};
                  {%- elsif value.swatch.image -%}--swatch:url({{ value.swatch.image | image_url: width: 120 }});
                  {%- else -%}
                    {%- assign vname = value | downcase -%}
                    {%- if vname contains 'nero' or vname contains 'black' -%}--swatch:#1a1a1a;
                    {%- elsif vname contains 'testa di moro' -%}--swatch:#3d1a0a;
                    {%- elsif vname contains 'marrone' or vname contains 'brown' -%}--swatch:#5c3317;
                    {%- else -%}--swatch:#d9d9d9;
                    {%- endif -%}
                  {%- endif -%}
                {%- endcapture -%}
                <button
                  type="button"
                  class="custom-buy-box__swatch{% if value.selected %} is-on{% endif %}"
                  data-swatch
                  data-value="{{ value | escape }}"
                  title="{{ value | escape }}"
                  aria-label="{{ value | escape }}"
                  style="{{ sw_style | strip_newlines | strip }}"
                ></button>
              {%- endfor -%}
            </div>
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}

        {%- if size_option -%}
          <div class="custom-buy-box__opt" data-size-opt data-pos="{{ size_option.position | minus: 1 }}">
            <p class="custom-buy-box__opt-label">
              {{ size_option.name | escape }}: <span data-size-value>{{ size_option.selected_value | escape }}</span>
            </p>
            <div class="custom-buy-box__pills">
              {%- for value in size_option.values -%}
                <button
                  type="button"
                  class="custom-buy-box__pill{% if value.selected %} is-on{% endif %}"
                  data-pill
                  data-value="{{ value | escape }}"
                >{{ value | escape }}</button>
              {%- endfor -%}
            </div>
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}

        {%- comment -%}
          Bottoni che aprono i due <dialog> (guida taglie / schede tecniche).
          data-open-dialog combacia con data-dialog sul <dialog>; logica in custom-buy-box.js.
        {%- endcomment -%}
        <div class="custom-buy-box__info-btns">
          <button type="button" class="custom-buy-box__info-btn" data-open-dialog="size">
            {%- comment -%} icona righello {%- endcomment -%}
            <svg class="custom-buy-box__info-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
              <path d="M21.3 15.3 8.7 2.7a1 1 0 0 0-1.4 0L2.7 7.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l12.6 12.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l4.6-4.6a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.4Z"/>
              <path d="m7.5 10.5 2 2M11 7l2 2M14.5 3.5l2 2M4 14l2 2"/>
            </svg>
            <span>{% if is_en %}Size guide{% else %}Guida taglie{% endif %}</span>
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="custom-buy-box__info-btn" data-open-dialog="specs">
            {%- comment -%} icona documento {%- endcomment -%}
            <svg class="custom-buy-box__info-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
              <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8Z"/>
              <path d="M14 2v6h6M8 13h8M8 17h8M8 9h2"/>
            </svg>
            <span>{% if is_en %}Spec sheets{% else %}Schede tecniche{% endif %}</span>
          </button>
        </div>

        {%- comment -%}
          Microcopy benefit sopra l'ATC: il gancio emozionale sta QUI, non nel
          bottone (CTA lunghe vanno a capo a 375px e diluiscono il verbo).
        {%- endcomment -%}
        <p class="custom-buy-box__atc-benefit">
          {%- if is_en -%}
            On your feet in 1 second. At your door in 48 hours.
          {%- else -%}
            Le infili in 1 secondo. Ai piedi in 48 ore.
          {%- endif -%}
        </p>

        {%- comment -%}
          Add to cart — clone scoped di `buy-buttons` con label custom
          (snippets/custom-buy-buttons.liquid): stesso <product-form> +
          {% form 'product' %} + product-form.js, cambia solo il testo.
          custom-buy-box.js aggiorna l'input name="id" al cambio variante.
        {%- endcomment -%}
        {%- liquid
          assign atc_label = 'Acquista Ora'
          if is_en
            assign atc_label = 'Buy Now'
          endif
        -%}
        {%- render 'custom-buy-buttons',
          product: product,
          product_form_id: product_form_id,
          section_id: section.id,
          label: atc_label
        -%}

        {%- comment -%}
          CTA secondaria sotto l'Acquista: apre WhatsApp con messaggio precompilato.
          Home -> niente URL prodotto, nome hardcoded; prezzo dalla prima variante
          (stesso first_variant usato per il prezzo a r.144), statico al load.
        {%- endcomment -%}
        {%- capture wa_message -%}
{%- if is_en -%}
Hi Dr Kampes, I'm interested in this product:

- Dr Kampes Trucker Shoes: {{ first_variant.price | money }}

I'd like some more information, thanks!
{%- else -%}
Ciao Dr Kampes, mi interessa questo prodotto:

- Dr Kampes Trucker Shoes: {{ first_variant.price | money }}

Vorrei chiederti piu' informazioni, grazie!
{%- endif -%}
{%- endcapture -%}
        {%- render 'whatsapp-info-button', message: wa_message -%}

        {%- comment -%}
          Righe trust sotto l'ATC: sempre visibili, non piu' accordion — il
          contenuto nascosto in un <details> chiuso non converte nessuno.
          Icona + claim in bold + coda breve; la versione lunga/emozionale
          resta nella sezione garanzie piu' sotto (ripetizione voluta).
          Icone stroke inline (niente stock Dawn fill-based, vedi rules.md).
        {%- endcomment -%}
        <ul class="custom-buy-box__trust">
          <li class="custom-buy-box__trust-row">
            <svg class="custom-buy-box__trust-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
              <path d="M3 9V5a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h16a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v4"/>
              <path d="M21 9H3l2 11a1 1 0 0 0 1 .8h12a1 1 0 0 0 1-.8Z"/>
              <path d="m9.5 14.5 2 2 3.5-3.5"/>
            </svg>
            <span>
              {%- if is_en -%}
                <strong>Free returns &amp; size exchange</strong> within 14 days, shipping on us
              {%- else -%}
                <strong>Reso e cambio taglia gratis</strong> entro 14 giorni, spedizione a nostro carico
              {%- endif -%}
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="custom-buy-box__trust-row">
            <svg class="custom-buy-box__trust-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
              <path d="M5 18H3a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h11a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v10"/>
              <path d="M15 8h4l3 4v5a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-1"/>
              <circle cx="7.5" cy="18" r="2"/>
              <circle cx="17.5" cy="18" r="2"/>
              <path d="M9.5 18H15"/>
            </svg>
            <span>
              {%- if is_en -%}
                <strong>Tracked express shipping</strong>, delivered in 1&ndash;2 business days
              {%- else -%}
                <strong>Spedizione tracciata</strong>, consegna in 1-2 giorni lavorativi
              {%- endif -%}
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="custom-buy-box__trust-row">
            <svg class="custom-buy-box__trust-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
              <path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.4 9.4 8 11 4.6-1.6 8-6 8-11V5Z"/>
              <path d="m8.5 12 2.5 2.5 4.5-4.5"/>
            </svg>
            <span>
              {%- if is_en -%}
                <strong>3-year warranty</strong>: structural failure? We repair or replace them
              {%- else -%}
                <strong>Garanzia 3 anni</strong>: se cedono, le ripariamo o sostituiamo
              {%- endif -%}
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="custom-buy-box__trust-row">
            <svg class="custom-buy-box__trust-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
              <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8Z"/>
              <path d="M14 2v6h6"/>
              <path d="m8.5 14.5 2 2 4-4"/>
            </svg>
            <span>
              {%- if is_en -%}
                <strong>S3S certified</strong> &middot; EN ISO 20345:2022+A1:2024, the top safety grade
              {%- else -%}
                <strong>Certificate S3S</strong> &middot; EN ISO 20345:2022+A1:2024, il grado massimo
              {%- endif -%}
            </span>
          </li>
        </ul>

      </div>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%}
      Sticky CTA: barra nera in basso con bottone, scivola su dopo 200px di scroll
      e si nasconde quando questa sezione (#acquista) e' in viewport.
      Logica in custom-buy-box.js. data-sticky-cta sulla barra (e' lei a slidare).
    {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="custom-buy-box__sticky-bar" data-sticky-cta>
      <a
        href="#acquista"
        class="custom-buy-box__sticky-cta button button--primary"
      >
        {{ section.settings.sticky_cta_label | escape }}
      </a>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%}
      Popup nativi <dialog> (top layer: niente conflitti z-index con sticky CTA/cart drawer).
      Contenuto hardcoded, portato 1:1 dal vecchio tema Horizon (home-buy-section.liquid).
      Apertura/chiusura in custom-buy-box.js. data-dialog combacia con data-open-dialog.
    {%- endcomment -%}
    <dialog
      id="cbb-dialog-size-{{ section.id }}"
      class="custom-buy-box__dialog"
      data-dialog="size"
      aria-labelledby="cbb-dialog-size-title-{{ section.id }}"
    >
      <div class="custom-buy-box__dialog-box">
        <button type="button" class="custom-buy-box__dialog-x" data-close-dialog aria-label="{% if is_en %}Close{% else %}Chiudi{% endif %}">&times;</button>
        <h3 class="custom-buy-box__dialog-title" id="cbb-dialog-size-title-{{ section.id }}">{% if is_en %}Size guide{% else %}Guida alla Taglia{% endif %}</h3>
        <div class="custom-buy-box__dialog-body">
          <p>{% if is_en %}Measure the inner insole length and compare it with the table.{% else %}Misura la lunghezza interna della soletta e confronta con la tabella.{% endif %}</p>
          <table class="custom-buy-box__stbl">
            <thead><tr><th>{% if is_en %}EU{% else %}IT{% endif %}</th><th>{% if is_en %}Inner insole (cm){% else %}Cm Soletta Interna{% endif %}</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>37</td><td>24,5 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>38</td><td>25 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>39</td><td>25,5 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>40</td><td>26,5 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>41</td><td>27,5 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>42</td><td>28 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>43</td><td>28,5 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>44</td><td>29 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>45</td><td>30 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>46</td><td>30,5 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>47</td><td>31 cm</td></tr>
              <tr><td>48</td><td>32 cm</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </dialog>

    <dialog
      id="cbb-dialog-specs-{{ section.id }}"
      class="custom-buy-box__dialog"
      data-dialog="specs"
      aria-labelledby="cbb-dialog-specs-title-{{ section.id }}"
    >
      <div class="custom-buy-box__dialog-box">
        <button type="button" class="custom-buy-box__dialog-x" data-close-dialog aria-label="{% if is_en %}Close{% else %}Chiudi{% endif %}">&times;</button>
        <h3 class="custom-buy-box__dialog-title" id="cbb-dialog-specs-title-{{ section.id }}">{% if is_en %}Technical documentation{% else %}Documentazione Tecnica{% endif %}</h3>
        <div class="custom-buy-box__dialog-body">
          <div class="custom-buy-box__doc-section">
            <p class="custom-buy-box__doc-label">{% if is_en %}Common documents{% else %}Documenti comuni{% endif %}</p>
            <a class="custom-buy-box__doc-row" href="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/DPI-DRKAMPES-CERTIFICAZIONE-S3S.pdf?v=1776677825" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-icon">&#8595;</span>
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-name">{% if is_en %}PPE S3S certification{% else %}Certificazione DPI S3S{% endif %}</span>
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-type">PDF</span>
            </a>
            <a class="custom-buy-box__doc-row" href="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/NOTA-INFORMATIVA-DRKAMPES.pdf?v=1776677825" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-icon">&#8595;</span>
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-name">{% if is_en %}Information notice{% else %}Nota informativa{% endif %}</span>
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-type">PDF</span>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="custom-buy-box__doc-section">
            <p class="custom-buy-box__doc-label">{% if is_en %}Spec sheets by model{% else %}Schede tecniche per modello{% endif %}</p>
            <a class="custom-buy-box__doc-row" href="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/DR_KAMPES_-_SCHEDA_TECNICA-20260420-BLACK.pdf?v=1776677825" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-icon">&#8595;</span>
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-name">{% if is_en %}Dr Kampes Black{% else %}Dr Kampes Nere{% endif %}</span>
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-type">PDF</span>
            </a>
            <a class="custom-buy-box__doc-row" href="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/DR_KAMPES_-_SCHEDA_TECNICA-20260420-BLACK.pdf?v=1776677825" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-icon">&#8595;</span>
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-name">{% if is_en %}Dr Kampes Dark Brown{% else %}Dr Kampes Testa di Moro{% endif %}</span>
              <span class="custom-buy-box__doc-type">PDF</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </dialog>

  </custom-buy-box>

  {%- comment -%} product-form.js: stesso caricamento di featured-product (guarded). {%- endcomment -%}
  <script src="{{ 'product-form.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
  <script src="{{ 'custom-buy-box.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
{%- endif -%}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "CUSTOM · Acquista",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "custom-buy-box-section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "product",
      "id": "product",
      "label": "Prodotto"
    },
    {
      "type": "color_scheme",
      "id": "color_scheme",
      "label": "Schema colore",
      "default": "scheme-1"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "sticky_cta_label",
      "label": "Testo bottone flottante",
      "default": "Acquista Ora"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    { "name": "CUSTOM · Acquista" }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
